<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink117">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi nalaṉē</l>
<l>iṉṉa tākutal koṭitē puṉṉai</l>
<l>yaṇimalar tuṟaitoṟum varikku</l>
<l>maṇinīrc cērppaṉai maṟavā tīmē</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Oh friend, listen!</l>
<l>It is harsh that [your] beauty has become like this.</l>
<l>Please do not forget the man from the shore with sapphire waters</l>
<l>Where beautiful Puṉṉai blossoms draw [patterns] throughout the ghat.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
